{
  "stem": "10768.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they were probably looking for dollars, so maybe other-- they were looking for smugglers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But since I had these few items that I bought for the 200 zloty, they first, they took this away from me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they told me to undress almost completely, to the point where there were-- if there was a little seam, they were trying on the seam if I don't have something sewn in.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And at that time, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] after they have taken away my items-- some of the personal belongings, too, but not too many, and they gave me back.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they said at 4 o'clock in the morning, we will take you to the water.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you behave quietly, because the Russians are on the other side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If they catch you, they will either send you home, or they will shoot you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in a way, they took everything away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were collaborating, apparently, with that man that they took us to a water, which was not above the knee.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The water was very cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was already December.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But somehow I made it on the other side of the river-- on the side of the river where the Russians were already-- into fields, which were familiar to me.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because as young children-- I was 12, 13 years old-- but we used to go very frequently to make gym there on the open fields, from school.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also, before I was dating, but still occasionally I went out with a boy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we went there walking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was familiar with these fields.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I crossed them over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was approximately 6 o'clock in the morning, when I came to the first house on this western outskirt of our city.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
